                            <i class="fas fa-info-circle me-2"></i>Introduction
                        </h2>
                        <p class="lead text-muted lh-lg">
                            ABC Retailers is committed to protecting the privacy of our customers. This privacy policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you shop on our website.
                        </p>
                    </div>
