                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-6">
                                <div class="usage-item p-3 border-start border-success border-4 bg-light">
                                    <h5 class="fw-bold text-dark mb-2">
                                        <i class="fas fa-comments text-success me-2"></i>Communication
