                                        You can access and update your personal information by logging into your account.
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="accordion-item border-0 mb-2">
                                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed bg-light border-0 rounded-3 fw-bold" type="button"
                                            data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#optOutRight">
                                        <span class="badge bg-secondary me-3">2</span>
